/--
Define a new custom target for the package. Has one form:

```lean
target «target-name» (pkg : Package) : α :=
  /- build function term -/
```

The `pkg` parameter (and its type specifier) is optional.
The term should be of type `IndexBuildM (BuildJob α)`.
-/
